     <h2>
      Welcome to the website of A.B.C. Childcare and Preschool
     </h2>
     <p>
      The primary goal of A.B.C. is to provide the 
			best possible care and service for you and your child. Our centers are one of the best environments in Greater 
			Cincinnati for your child to learn and grow in.
     </p>
     <p>
      <b>
       Here are just a few reasons why:
      </b>
     </p>
     <p>
     </p>
     <ul>
      <li>
       We are a loving, caring and educated teaching team
      </li>
      <li>
       We have an "Open Door" policy for all enrolled families
      </li>
      <li>
       We offer developmentally appropriate activities
      </li>
      <li>
       We recognize the need to work with parents as a team
      </li>
      <li>
       We encourage self-esteem and positive thinking
      </li>
      <li>
       We follow all laws and guidelines issued by the State of Ohio
      </li>
      <li>
       We are licensed by the State of Ohio
      </li>
     </ul>
     <p>
     </p>
     <p>
      We are here to learn and grow with you and your family and our doors are always open for visits and 
			participation. If you should ever need assistance in any way, please do not hesitate to call or stop in and see 
			one of our Administrators or myself. We look forward to having you as a part of our family.
     </p>
